## Why Email Marketing Matters for Restaurants

For a small business restaurant owner, choosing the right email marketing platform can be a big boost to your revenue. According to a report by MailChimp, restaurants saw the following email metrics in 2019:

- Open rates – 19.77%
- Average click rate – 1.34%
- Unsubscribe rate – 0.28%

